"{\"uid\": \"actionnews5.com-2024-08-08-breakdancing-makes-olympics-debut-2024-games\", \"noun_phrases\": [{\"sentence\": \"MEMPHIS, Tenn. (WMC) - There is a \\\"throw down\\\" happening at the Paris Olympics, and it's a first, as breakdancing makes its debut at the 2024 games.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 148, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"MEMPHIS\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 7}, {\"ngram\": \"Tenn. (WMC\", \"from\": 9, \"to\": 19}, {\"ngram\": \"the Paris Olympics\", \"from\": 60, \"to\": 78}, {\"ngram\": \"its debut\", \"from\": 120, \"to\": 129}, {\"ngram\": \"the 2024 games\", \"from\": 133, \"to\": 147}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Whether they are \\\"power heads\\\" or \\\"footwork cats,\\\" b-boys and b-girls from around the world answered the \\\"call out\\\" to show their moves on a global stage.\", \"from\": 150, \"to\": 304, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"\\\"power heads\", \"from\": 167, \"to\": 179}, {\"ngram\": \"\\\"footwork cats\", \"from\": 184, \"to\": 198}, {\"ngram\": \"b\", \"from\": 201, \"to\": 202}, {\"ngram\": \"boys\", \"from\": 203, \"to\": 207}, {\"ngram\": \"b\", \"from\": 212, \"to\": 213}, {\"ngram\": \"girls\", \"from\": 214, \"to\": 219}, {\"ngram\": \"the world\", \"from\": 232, \"to\": 241}, {\"ngram\": \"the \\\"call\", \"from\": 251, \"to\": 260}, {\"ngram\": \"their moves\", \"from\": 274, \"to\": 285}, {\"ngram\": \"a global stage\", \"from\": 289, \"to\": 303}]}, {\"sentence\": \"We met up with a couple of Memphis breakers to learn how those \\\"super crews\\\" might put together their \\\"sets\\\" at the Olympics.\", \"from\": 306, \"to\": 431, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 333, \"end\": 340, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Memphis_Tigers_football\", \"score\": 0.759958702094541, \"rank\": 0.2245538848149696, \"text\": \"Memphis\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Memphis_Tigers_football\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Memphis_Tigers_football\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a couple\", \"from\": 321, \"to\": 329}, {\"ngram\": \"those \\\"super crews\", \"from\": 363, \"to\": 381}, {\"ngram\": \"their \\\"sets\", \"from\": 402, \"to\": 413}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympics\", \"from\": 418, \"to\": 430}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Brandon Marshall, known as \\\"B-boy Nosey\\\" in his Illville Crew, has been breaking for about 23 years.\", \"from\": 433, \"to\": 533, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 433, \"end\": 449, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brandon_Marshall\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 8.113696284849712e-21, \"text\": \"Brandon Marshall\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q14128148\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brandon_Marshall\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brandon_Marshall\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"\\\"B-boy Nosey\", \"from\": 460, \"to\": 472}, {\"ngram\": \"his Illville Crew\", \"from\": 477, \"to\": 494}, {\"ngram\": \"about 23 years\", \"from\": 518, \"to\": 532}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"But when I was 14-15 years old and I got into high school, it was a way for me to impress girls and just impress my classmates and things,\\\" he explained about his start with the dance genre.\", \"from\": 535, \"to\": 726, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"high school\", \"from\": 582, \"to\": 593}, {\"ngram\": \"a way\", \"from\": 602, \"to\": 607}, {\"ngram\": \"girls\", \"from\": 626, \"to\": 631}, {\"ngram\": \"my classmates\", \"from\": 649, \"to\": 662}, {\"ngram\": \"things\", \"from\": 667, \"to\": 673}, {\"ngram\": \"his start\", \"from\": 695, \"to\": 704}, {\"ngram\": \"the dance genre\", \"from\": 710, \"to\": 725}]}, {\"sentence\": \"We caught up with \\\"B-boy Nosey\\\" and \\\"B-girl Nana\\\" Tsujikawa at New Ballet Ensemble and School of Dance in Midtown Memphis, founded by Katie Smythe in 2002 \\\"to address the lack of access to excellence in dance.\\\"\", \"from\": 728, \"to\": 938, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 772, \"end\": 776, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Akan_chieftaincy\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.326996668248361e-15, \"text\": \"Nana\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Akan_chieftaincy\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Akan_chieftaincy\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"B-boy Nosey\", \"from\": 747, \"to\": 758}, {\"ngram\": \"New Ballet Ensemble\", \"from\": 791, \"to\": 810}, {\"ngram\": \"School\", \"from\": 815, \"to\": 821}, {\"ngram\": \"Dance\", \"from\": 825, \"to\": 830}, {\"ngram\": \"Midtown Memphis\", \"from\": 834, \"to\": 849}, {\"ngram\": \"Katie Smythe\", \"from\": 862, \"to\": 874}, {\"ngram\": \"the lack\", \"from\": 895, \"to\": 903}, {\"ngram\": \"access\", \"from\": 907, \"to\": 913}, {\"ngram\": \"excellence\", \"from\": 917, \"to\": 927}, {\"ngram\": \"dance\", \"from\": 931, \"to\": 936}]}, {\"sentence\": \"And that includes \\\"street dancing\\\" likejookin'and breaking.\", \"from\": 940, \"to\": 999, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"street dancing\", \"from\": 959, \"to\": 973}, {\"ngram\": \"likejookin'and breaking\", \"from\": 975, \"to\": 998}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Katie found us when I was about 18 years old and allowed us--me and my friends--to come here and practice for free,\\\" B-boy Nosey said.\", \"from\": 1001, \"to\": 1136, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1125, \"end\": 1130, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Intrusiveness\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Nosey\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Intrusiveness\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Intrusiveness\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Katie\", \"from\": 1002, \"to\": 1007}, {\"ngram\": \"us\", \"from\": 1014, \"to\": 1016}, {\"ngram\": \"us\", \"from\": 1059, \"to\": 1061}, {\"ngram\": \"my friends\", \"from\": 1070, \"to\": 1080}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"And she provided a space for our community.\", \"from\": 1137, \"to\": 1181, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a space\", \"from\": 1155, \"to\": 1162}, {\"ngram\": \"our community\", \"from\": 1167, \"to\": 1180}]}, {\"sentence\": \"So a big part of my success I definitely owe to Katie and the New Ballet Ensemble.\\\"\", \"from\": 1182, \"to\": 1265, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"So a big part\", \"from\": 1182, \"to\": 1195}, {\"ngram\": \"my success\", \"from\": 1199, \"to\": 1209}, {\"ngram\": \"Katie\", \"from\": 1230, \"to\": 1235}, {\"ngram\": \"the New Ballet Ensemble\", \"from\": 1240, \"to\": 1263}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Breakdancing actually started in the Bronx decades ago.\", \"from\": 1267, \"to\": 1322, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1304, \"end\": 1309, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Bronx\", \"score\": 0.9999999990357082, \"rank\": 9.641643319227476e-10, \"text\": \"Bronx\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Bronx\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Bronx\"}], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Breaking is one of the four main pillars of hip hop culture, which is this folk culture that we invented here in America in New York City in the 70s,\\\" Nosey said.\", \"from\": 1324, \"to\": 1487, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1449, \"end\": 1462, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_York_City\", \"score\": 0.9999999999995453, \"rank\": 4.428942474102487e-13, \"text\": \"New York City\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_York_City\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_York_City\"}, {\"begin\": 1476, \"end\": 1481, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Intrusiveness\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Nosey\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Intrusiveness\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Intrusiveness\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the four main pillars\", \"from\": 1344, \"to\": 1365}, {\"ngram\": \"hip hop culture\", \"from\": 1369, \"to\": 1384}